highlights.text: The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Blinding Lights” is the highest at #50.
“Step Into Christmas” by Elton John is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 85 spots at #36.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 255 weeks straight.
